---
<div class="bg-white p-4 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto h-max px-6 md:px-12 xl:px-6">
        <div class="w-full flex items-center flex-col gap-1 justify-center mb-16 px-4">
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600">Como Trabajamos?</p>
            <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-center font-semibold">Te acompañamos durante todo el proceso</h3>
        </div>
        <div
                class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-black/20 overflow-hidden rounded-sm border-[1.2px] border-white/20 dark:border-black/20 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-4">
            <div class="group relative transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
                <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
                    <svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round"
                         stroke-linejoin="round" color="white" style="color:black" height="50" width="50"
                         xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path>
